Question: AIROHA Technology CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Airoha Technology

Product: AG3335MA Satellite Positioning Chip Series

- Passed AEC-Q100 Grade 2 reliability qualification tests for automotive applications
- Ultra-low power consumption, high endurance, dual-frequency capability
- Supports five major global satellite systems and NavIC
- Professional-grade GNSS receiver measurement engine with ultra-low satellite tracking sensitivity of -167 dBm
- Extremely short cold boot positioning time of 25 seconds
- Internationally leading signal frequency support capability
- Operates reliably in extreme environments, ranging from -40 to 105 degrees Celsius
- Actively pursuing ISO 26262 automotive functional safety process and product certification
- Successfully integrated with parent company MediaTek's Dimensity Auto platform
- Provides highly integrated solutions and technical testing services to automotive manufacturers worldwide
